[Nouns] idolatry, idolism; demonism, demonolatry; idol-worship, demon-worship, devil-worship, fire-worship; zoolatry, fetichism; ecclesiolatry, heliolatry, Mariolatry, Bibliolatry.
deification, apotheosis, canonization; hero worship.
sacrifices, hecatomb, holocaust; human sacrifices, immolation, mactation, infanticde, self-immolation, suttee.
idol, golden calf, graven image, fetich, avatar, Juggernath, lares et penates; Baal [more].
[Verbs] worship idols, worship pictures, worship relics; deify, canonize.
[Adjectives] idolatrous.
